Van Damme, aka "The Muscles From Brussels," has listed his three-story home on the Grand Canal in Los Angeles' Marina del Rey area for $9,999,000. He paid $6 million for the newly built 6-bedroom, 11-bathroom home in 2012 — which, coincidentally, is the same year he co-starred alongside Sylvester Stallone in "The Expendables 2."
